narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend it to students who is in retested in economics and time series.
This course talks about important theories about time series. Worth taking.
Very technical course, but great quality and teaching.
A more than required class for any students working in econometrics. A lot of fascinating and helpful material.

I'd recommend the course to the student if they were prepared for the unusual style.
